{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nEmbark on a voyage of ultimate luxury and exploration aboard the Lagoon 450F “Amelia” catamaran. This exceptional vessel merges comfort, performance, and elegance, promising an unparalleled sailing experience that will leave you in awe of the open seas.\n\nCrafted Elegance: “Amelia” stands as a testament to meticulous design and craftsmanship. From its graceful exterior lines to its well-appointed interior spaces, every aspect reflects a commitment to delivering an extraordinary journey on the water.\n\nKey Features:\n\nSpacious Design for Comfort: “Amelia” offers an abundance of space, ensuring every moment aboard is marked by comfort and relaxation. With spacious cabins and inviting common areas, this catamaran invites you to unwind and revel in the beauty of your surroundings.\n\nPanoramic Views: Immerse yourself in the world outside through “Amelia’s” panoramic windows. Whether you’re in the salon or your private cabin, the stunning vistas of the sea will be a constant reminder of the incredible journey you’re undertaking.\n\nModern Amenities: Experience modern living even while at sea. “Amelia” boasts a range of amenities that cater to your needs, from a fully equipped kitchen to entertainment systems, ensuring that your voyage is as enjoyable as it is luxurious.\n\nOutdoor Delights: Step onto the spacious deck of “Amelia” and feel the sea breeze on your skin. With ample outdoor seating and lounging areas, including a stunning flybridge, you can bask in the sun, socialize, and enjoy al fresco dining with breathtaking ocean views.\n\nAs you set sail on the Lagoon 450F “Amelia,” you’re not merely embarking on a journey; you’re entering a realm where luxury and adventure intertwine. This catamaran promises an experience that surpasses expectations, with its refined design, modern amenities, and spaces that invite you to savor every moment on the water. Get ready to create memories that will forever define your perception of what sailing can be.\n","blueprint":{"name":"AMELIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae2fa7c0-413b-11f0-abb1-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae3af260-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae388160-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae304401-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae2fced0-413b-11f0-abb1-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae304400-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae2ff5e0-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae2ebd60-413b-11f0-abb1-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae33c670-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae3aa440-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae30b930-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae773810-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae6c89b0-413b-11f0-abb2-5786c1f212e6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5ccccc2-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae769bd0-413b-11